name: Kenwood Food Processor, White - FP691
short_description: The Kenwood FP691 Food Processor helps cut down on time spent on cooking. This food processor features a simple design that makes it easy to use on a daily basis. It boasts a compact overall size with one variable speed outlet for slow or high speed attachments. A 1.5L bowl lets you process large quantities of food in one go. You can use the 1.5L liquidizer container to make juices, smoothies, soups, purees, and milkshakes. The included multi mill lets you prepare curry pastes, chopped herbs as well as chopped nuts. You can use the stainless steel chopping blade to chop meat and vegetables, blend cake mixes, as well as to make delicious dips. The dough tool lets you make your own bread. This processor is designed with various built in failsafe mechanisms that actively as well as passively prevent messes and mishaps.

short_description: The Kenwood FP120 Compact Food Processor is ideal for those who only process small quantities, or who have limited worktop/storage space. With a single speed and pulse function, this is a simple-to-use model and is ideal for first time users. It offers the versatility of a standard food processor, with 13 different functions, but takes up less space. The FP120 features a full safety interlock and a maxi blend canopy, which increases capacity by 30%, even in smaller processor bowls. The FP120 has an 800 g capacity for cakes and 800 ml for liquisa, using the maxi blend canopy. The Kenwood Compact FP120 has a 400 W motor, a 1.4 Litre bowl and various other attachments, including stainless steel chopping blade, thick slicer plate, coarse shredder plate and whisk tool. Other key features of the FP120 include dishwasher safe parts for easy cleaning, rubberised feet for safety and added stability and Easywind cord storage
